        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Hi friends \xf0\x9f\x91\x8b,
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Happy new year! Hope you all enjoyed your holidays, got to relax and recharge a little bit, and, if you live in New York, that your COVID wasn\xe2\x80\x99t too bad.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Last year, for the first piece of the year, I came out swinging with my only-ever
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkEluxCAQRU_T7GIxtmHBIptcAzFU26QxWBjH8u1Dt6VEqkGqUtXXf942mEo99Vq2hl7FtHMFneHYErQGFe0bVBODJncqmeAKBc0DkUKiuJlHBVhsTLrVHdC6uxS9bbHk9wXGVKBZS3gw6YXyANgGFWR4KMKEo8SPlAVx6do9RMgeNPxAPUsGlPTc2rrd2OeNfvU4jmPIpblSY54GX_po7eliSh_2w4GtKGqKKcUEM8IxF3Sgg7cjVhiA3Ak46WG4fys1-mm-cbxMdNh2tzXrn_3hgqr-E-jr52wXSO9Ft2Z6X_Yc22kgW5cgXK7bBe_NwUyQoXaowdjWkXFCiRwxk1RdLjsW_ppijlFXDqVf5X_RX-wGhqk" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          bear case on Bill.com
         </a>
         . I was hilariously wrong on the stock: it opened that morning at $137.46 and a year later, it\xe2\x80\x99s up 81.25% to $249.15. It handily outperformed the NASDAQ (+22.3%) and the BVP Cloud Index (-1.8%). It grew revenue 151.9% last year, faster than any other BVP Cloud Index company by far (Snowflake is second at 109.5%). Just clobbered me.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         I learned a few lessons from that:
        </p>
        <ol style="margin-top: 0;">
         <li style="margin-bottom: 3.75px; margin-left: 7.5px; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 3.75px;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">
           Never underestimate strong distribution, even in the face of a shitty product.
          </p>
         </li>
         <li style="margin-bottom: 3.75px; margin-left: 7.5px; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 3.75px;">
          <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">
           Kick the year off optimistically.
          </p>
         </li>
        </ol>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         And whew, there\xe2\x80\x99s a lot to cover! I go away for a couple weeks and an all-out war over what web3 is and isn\xe2\x80\x99t, who owns it and who doesn\xe2\x80\x99t, and whether or not it\xe2\x80\x99s total bullshit breaks out.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         You know where I come out on this, but words are words. Actions speak louder.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Let\xe2\x80\x99s get to it.
        </p>
        <div style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;">
