        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Importantly, the digital pieces have value. The total crypto market cap passed $3 trillion this year. ConstitutionDAO raised $47 million. These three pictures are worth over $18 million. There\xe2\x80\x99s real money on the line, which makes people behave like it\xe2\x80\x99s the real thing.
        </p>
        <div class="captioned-image-container-static" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center;">
         <figure style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;">
