        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         <em>
          Complexity Economics: A Different Framework for Economic Thought, Brian Arthur
         </em>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Beyond math versus simulation, there were a number of major differences between Arthur\xe2\x80\x99s complexity economics and neoclassical economics. In a January 2021
         <em>
          Nature
         </em>
         article,
         <em>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkEuOwyAMhk9Tdo0MIa8Fi9nMNSIH3JRpAhE4E-X2Q5vFSJZt-fXLn0WmOabTbDGzeLuRz41MoCMvxExJ7JnS6J2RrerrRg_CGe1k3_TC5_GRiFb0i-G0k9j2afEW2cfw2QBQjXgaZ7sy37RWTj1gD06i0g_UyqGdHLaXLu7OU7Bk6JfSGQOJxTyZt3yrv27qu9hxHFVA3hNVNq6lgIm9XSiXNGulGn0HBfei2tX3WnijQCmQUEsNulGVqix2MACRbCVNvaWq_RmGzs7Pm4Z1VlXep8xoX-_7IpkQeYrJh7m0X09cafk0yptjiesePJ8jBZwWchcBvkB-mIwzBUoFsBuRCz4tlew7qHs1XB8XRPpdBQ2iKLtYtsK_6B-te4iL" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           Foundations of Complexity Economics
          </a>
          ,
         </em>
         he laid those differences out, feature-by-feature.
        </p>
