        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         But what if they didn\xe2\x80\x99t have to be little dots or bits of code, simpler than human beings? What if they could
         <em>
          be
         </em>
         human beings?
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
